1. *Pomogne* mi da se prebacim na drugu stranu reci. (He helped me to cross to the other side of the river.)
2. Ona mu je *pomogla* da dobije posao. (She helped him to get the job.)
3. Uvek se trudim da *pomognem* ljudima u nevolji. (I always strive to help people in need.)
4. Ona mu je *pomogla* da dobije posao. (He helped her to get the job.)
5. *Pomognite* mi da izgradim kucu. (Help me to build a house.)